not oblit-</div><div class="t m97 x31 h13 y7b7 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">erated; rightly understood, nature speaks of her Creator.&quot;â€”Chrise </div><div class="t m24d x7f h13 y52 ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">s Object </div><div class="t md4 x31 h13 y7b8 ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons, </div><div class="t mb3 x7b h13 y7b8 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 18. </div><div class="t m2e4 x31 h1d y1c5 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: &quot;Speak to the earth, and it shall teach thee: and </div><div class="t m49a x31 h1d y7b9 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the fishes of the sea shall declare unto thee. Who knoweth not in all </div><div class="t m311 x31 h1d y7ba ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these that the hand of the Lord hath wrought this?&quot; (Job 12:8, 9). </div><div class="t mba x31 h1d y7bb ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THEME: </div><div class="t m286 x95 h13 y7bc ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Observation of the natural world opens a treasury of information </div><div class="t m2d7 x31 h13 y7bd ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the keen searcher for truth: practical, scientific, and spiritual. </div><div class="t mbd x4a h1d y7be ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OUTLINE: </div><div class="t m6b x4f h1d y7bf ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. </div><div class="t me7 x5d h1d y1cc ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons From Life Science (Prov. 6:6-11). </div><div class="t mbf x13 h1d y7c0 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II. </div><div class="t m2ef x5d h1d y7c0 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons From Physical Science (Prov. 3:19, 20; Ps. 19:1-6). </div><div class="t mc0 x19 h1d y7c1 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">III. </div><div class="t m1a4 x5d h1d y7c1 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Creative Masterpiece (Ps. 8:3-5; Prov. 8:22-31). </div><div class="t m114 x4a h1d y7c2 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. LESSONS FROM LIFE SCIENCE (Prov. 6:6-11). </div><div class="t me6 x49 h13 y3a9 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">By connecting truth with familiar objects we are reminded afresh, with </div><div class="t m19b x1a h13 y7c3 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 l